name: Black Metal Girl
description: Stumped on what to give Grandma or youth leader at church? Worry no more as, Black Metal Girl is here! This dark goddess has been crafted using two sheets of clear acetate, separately drawn with the highest quality sharpies that the dark lord has to offer, and then brought together in unholy union, slightly askew, to the shrieking delight of our house warlock. Lastly, this murderous beauty has been entombed for eternity with a deceptively white mat and pitch black frame. Don't hesitate and buy this ing√©nue before she slips into the ever-blackening void!!

name: Mugshot Girl
description: Treat your loved one or yourself to this 8 x 11 hand drawn inebriated beauty. Using the finest sharpies that I can find in the dump,  I  loving sketched this mugshot babe on two separate transparencies, which I then merged into an sticky-fumbling eye-candy orgy. To top it off, this bad girl has been matted and framed for immediate hanging in your boudoir, dining area or garage. Don't miss out, because when she is sent to county, she may never look the same.

name: Wank-A-Thon
